<p>If you’re studying for an undergraduate or master's degree and interested in teaching, an internship could help you to understand what it’s really like in the classroom.</p>

<p>Internships last 3 weeks, start in June or July and you’ll be paid from <%= v :teachinginternship_weekly %> per week.</p>

<p>Find out how to apply, including details of teaching internship providers in each region, further down this page.</p>

